l 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 23:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-discover-strange-narwhal-waves-that-trap-light-beyond-known-limits</guid></item></channel></rss>